herpderp for irssi

Randomly replaces text sent by people/to channels in a list with nonsense words like "herp" and "derp"
Do you find someone annoying? Why use IGNORE when you can use herpderp.pl and let them amuse you!

author:  neofreak@irc.ptnet.org
 email: igotbugs@ticklemynausea.net 
   web: http://www.ticklemynausea.net

