Usage:
/herp list                : show a list of all nicks in the herpderp list
/herp add [nick|#channel] : adds a nickname/channel to the herpderp list
/herp del [nick|#channel] : removes a nickname/channel from the herpderp list
/herp all                 : toggles herpderping all incoming messages
